      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the premium price of a mint-condition model.",
