    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home. This car has been so good to me\u2014it\u2019s in great shape, runs like a dream, and is super comfy for those long weekend trips! I\u2019ve kept up with all the basics, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road whenever you are. It\u2019s a solid, reliable choice that still has tons of life left in it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
