    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Turbo features the legendary Mezger-designed 3.6L twin-turbocharged flat-six, delivering power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional mechanical grip, complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a full cooling system overhaul with pinned coolant lines and a fresh set of Bilstein coilovers to maintain chassis composure. The Brembo four-piston monoblock calipers provide firm pedal feel and consistent thermal management. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust with strong boost pressure and no signs of rear main seal leaks.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, accented by clean alloy wheels and clear lenses, though a few minor stone chips exist from highway travel. Open the door to find an interior that reflects pride of ownership: the upholstery is clean and supple, the carpets have been protected by floor mats, and the cabin remains free of any odors. Every button and switch operates as intended, including the responsive infotainment system and dual-zone climate control. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefiting from a strict adherence to the manufacturer\u2019s maintenance schedule. With a recent brake service and fresh tires, this car offers a confident and smooth driving experience. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for the road ahead.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
