    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a synthesis of performance and long-term value. Exhibiting a sophisticated aesthetic and robust mechanical integrity, this automobile has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our authoritative standards for quality and reliability. It offers a refined driving experience and remains a distinguished example of its class, presenting an exceptional acquisition opportunity for those who prioritize excellence in a pre-owned investment.",
      "price": 36500.0,
