    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014absolutely perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, and while it\u2019s definitely seen some adventures, it\u2019s still got so much life left to give. It's super reliable and ready for its next chapter with a new owner. Come take it for a spin, I just know you're going to love it!",
