    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the S65 4.0L V8\u2014a high-revving masterpiece featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for precise power delivery. Critically, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed, mitigating common S65 failure points and ensuring the valvetrain remains robust. The chassis retains its factory Electronic Damping Control (EDC) functionality, providing excellent lateral grip and composure through the corners. While the cosmetic condition reflects its status as a well-maintained driver's car, the drivetrain and subframe remain tight and responsive. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist seeking a naturally aspirated atmospheric icon.",
